data.eligibility_criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

1. Signed and dated IEC-approved Informed Consent.
2. Diagnosis of sinonasal tumor with the following histotypes:

   * Squamous Cell Carcinoma (SCC);
   * Sinonasal Undifferentiated Carcinoma (SNUC);
   * Small Cell Carcinoma Neuroendocrine Type (SmCCNET);
   * Pure Sinonasal N

Inclusion Criteria:

* Signed the informed consent form prior to patient entry;
* ECOG PS：0-2;Expected Survival Time: Over 3 months;
* EGFR、ALK、ROS1 mutation-negative；Patients with squamous cell carcinoma may not have genetic testing;
* Diagnosed with advanced NSCLC (phase IIIB/IV) through pathology
